# this is demo to tell you  how to use BaseServiceProcee class which processing signal in multithreaded

1. how to use in code
NOTES: the  only  things we should do is create instance of BaseServiceProcess at begin of main function, then call the member function installSigignalHandle();
e.g:
	BaseServiceProcee test;
	test.installSigignalHandle();

2. get properties file
sudo kill -60 `pgrep signal_example`
sleep 10
sudo kill -61 `pgrep signal_example`
file: /tmp/nros.profile

3. transport *.profile to pdf or png
pprof --pdf signal_example /tmp/nros.profile >>nros.pdf

4. kill signal_example
sudo kill -9 `pgrep signal_example`

# good luck
